PathOfBuilding.Notes:
Note: Projectile Weakness can be moved to the main curse 4-link in place of Spell Cascade, however this will reduce the mana cost of Frostbite and require you to lower your rank of Arcane Surge to compensate. In exchange you will need to refresh your Sniper's Mark less frequently on bosses, however I suspect the default duration of ~10 seconds is more than enough by itself. Prior to anointing Whispers of Doom, it's still better to use Sniper's Mark on bosses, but you may want to still be in the habit of casting Frostbite -> Sniper's Mark to continue to refresh Arcane Surge and ensure that Sniper's Mark is applied second (and thus not overwritten by Frostbite until you have +1 to maximum curses).
Note: "Basic Clusters" setup is to give an idea of what decent but non-ideal clusters might look like prior to a high investment setup that would include an Atziri's Reflection and other high cost gear changes. See the "high end PoB example" in the forum guide for what a high investment setup might look like.
